# Environment Variables Template
# 
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# Copy this file to .env.production for production deployment
# DO NOT commit .env.local or .env.production to git
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in all required values from your services
# 3. For production, also create .env.production with production values
# 4. Verify setup: npm run verify:prod-env

# ============================================================================
# ANTHROPIC API - Claude AI Integration
# ============================================================================
# Get from: https://console.anthropic.com/account/keys
# Used for: AI Bestie and AI Wingman response generation
# Required: YES
# Format: sk-ant-api03-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ============================================================================
# SUPABASE - Database and Backend Services
# ============================================================================
# Get these from your Supabase project settings > API
# https://app.supabase.com/project/[project-id]/settings/api
# Required: YES for all

# Public URL for client-side Supabase initialization
# Format: https://your-project.supabase.co
PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co

# Public anonymous key for client-side operations
# Format: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here

# Server-side URL for backend operations
# Format: https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co

# Service role key for server-side operations (KEEP SECRET)
# Used for: AI assistant conversations, profile management, RLS-protected operations
# Format: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# ============================================================================
# VOYAGE AI - Vector Embeddings for Semantic Search
# ============================================================================
# Get from: https://dash.voyageai.com/api-keys
# Used for: Semantic search and embeddings for match context
# Required: NO (optional, but recommended for better search)
# Format: pa-...
VOYAGE_API_KEY=pa-...

# ============================================================================
# FIREBASE CLOUD MESSAGING - Push Notifications
# ============================================================================
# Get from: Firebase Console > Project Settings > Cloud Messaging > Server key
# Used for: Sending push notifications to Android/iOS devices via FCM HTTP API
# Required: YES (for push notification delivery)
# Format: AAAA...
FCM_SERVER_KEY=your-fcm-server-key-here

# ============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Development and Testing
# ============================================================================
# Skip SvelteKit verification during development (optional)
# Set to true for faster development builds
# VITE_SKIP_VERIFICATION=true

# Seed account password for testing (optional)
# Used for creating test accounts during development
# SEED_ACCOUNT_PASSWORD=SeedPass123!

# ============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Plane Integration (Project Management)
# ============================================================================
# Get from: https://app.plane.so/settings/api-tokens
# Used for: Creating and managing project tickets
# PLANE_API_KEY=plane_api_...
# PLANE_WORKSPACE=your-workspace
# PLANE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id

# ============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: FAL AI Integration (Image Generation)
# ============================================================================
# Get from: https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
# Used for: Image generation and processing
# FAL_KEY=your-fal-key-here

# ============================================================================
# VERIFICATION
# ============================================================================
# After setting up environment variables, run:
#   npm run verify:prod-env
#
# This will verify:
# - All required variables are set
# - Supabase connectivity
# - Claude API connectivity
# - Database tables exist
#
# For more information, see: DEPLOYMENT.md
